for his future aspirations.

337
00:21:35,037 --> 00:21:36,806
I'll try talking to him,

338
00:21:37,740 --> 00:21:41,277
but he's been a real brat lately.

339
00:21:42,378 --> 00:21:44,280
-I'll pour you some tea.
-Thank you.

340
00:21:45,648 --> 00:21:47,416
Oh, that's right.

341
00:21:48,017 --> 00:21:50,720
