have been shutting me out.

347
00:22:07,036 --> 00:22:08,571
-Huh?
-Actually…

348
00:22:09,438 --> 00:22:13,843
I lost my login password,
and I'm getting it reissued.

349
00:22:13,909 --> 00:22:15,044
