explaining what happened to the parents.

362
00:23:15,171 --> 00:23:16,605
Yes, I will do that.

363
00:23:17,239 --> 00:23:18,474
I'm sorry.

364
00:23:18,541 --> 00:23:20,943
Have a good day!

365
00:23:23,112 --> 00:23:24,080
