374
00:23:47,703 --> 00:23:49,738
Or "we need to talk."

375
00:23:49,805 --> 00:23:51,507
Or "we need to talk."

376
00:23:51,574 --> 00:23:52,675
You know?

377
00:23:54,677 --> 00:23:56,011
"We need to talk."

