388
00:24:33,349 --> 00:24:35,117
It's the one I wanted.

389
00:24:37,820 --> 00:24:40,923
I'm going camping with a coworker,

390
00:24:40,990 --> 00:24:43,192
and I got put in charge.

391
00:24:44,693 --> 00:24:46,395
You're a good cook after all.

392
00:24:47,329 --> 00:24:51,667
When I was looking for tools I needed,
I remembered when we went camping.

393
00:24:52,368 --> 00:24:53,469
You know,

394
00:24:54,803 --> 00:24:56,005
