and dropped chopsticks in the river.

396
00:25:03,879 --> 00:25:05,881
Oh, yeah, I remember!

397
00:25:06,715 --> 00:25:08,350
So when I look at these,

398
00:25:09,318 --> 00:25:11,020
I want to buy one for you too.

