00:25:11,887 --> 00:25:15,758
I'd wonder what color you'd like.

400
00:25:16,325 --> 00:25:20,396
Or think about buying a third
or fourth if we start a family.

401
00:25:22,932 --> 00:25:24,033
So…

402
00:25:26,001 --> 00:25:26,835
Um…

403
00:25:30,139 --> 00:25:30,973
