00:25:33,676 --> 00:25:34,610
What?

405
00:25:35,711 --> 00:25:37,213
So I couldn't wait!

406
00:25:40,549 --> 00:25:42,751
Sorry, a lot's been going on,

407
00:25:44,353 --> 00:25:47,690
so I didn't have time to choose,
this is a placeholder!

