422
00:26:34,770 --> 00:26:35,604
Come with me.

423
00:26:35,671 --> 00:26:37,172
Hurry up!

424
00:26:37,239 --> 00:26:38,474
What the hell?

425
00:26:38,540 --> 00:26:40,643
-Come on already!
-Drink and do what?

426
00:26:41,377 --> 00:26:44,146
Drink like this… Just come with me!

427
00:26:44,947 --> 00:26:47,916
-Hurry up!
-Hold on!

428
00:26:47,983 --> 00:26:51,287
