00:27:50,913 --> 00:27:52,147
Kawai.

449
00:27:52,214 --> 00:27:56,985
So the girl you were gabbing away with
before our important meeting

450
00:27:57,052 --> 00:28:00,422
making me worry about how your
brain works, was your fiancé?

451
00:28:01,156 --> 00:28:02,024
