468
00:28:52,274 --> 00:28:53,876
-One second.
-Shotaro.

469
00:28:53,942 --> 00:28:54,810
They need you.

470
00:28:58,714 --> 00:28:59,982
Hijiri.

471
00:29:01,784 --> 00:29:02,885
Here you go.

472
00:29:04,553 --> 00:29:05,821
For the engagement.

473
00:29:07,022 --> 00:29:08,357
Thank you.

