-Liar.

492
00:30:17,259 --> 00:30:18,460
It's one or the other.

493
00:30:18,527 --> 00:30:20,462
-Come on, drink.
-I'm driving.

494
00:30:21,930 --> 00:30:24,299
Someone once said,

495
00:30:24,366 --> 00:30:28,904
"Love kills happiness
and happiness kills love."

496
00:30:30,339 --> 00:30:31,373
